        "\"\"\"#### **Quartiles of Feature Age**\n",
        "\"\"\"\n",
        "\"\"\"Explanation\n",
        "age_q1 = np.quantile(data['Age'], 0.25)\n",
        "The 0.25 means 25%.\n",
        "Python asks:\n",
        "\n",
        "\"What age separates the first 25% of passengers from the remaining 75%?\"\n",
        "\n",
        "Suppose our ages are:\n",
        "5  12  18  22  25  30  35  40\n",
        "\n",
        "25% of 8 passengers = 2 passengers.\n",
        "5 12 | 18 22 25 30 35 40\n",
        "The cut value (Q1) is approximately 15 (between 12 and 18).\n",
        "means:\n",
        "\n",
        "25% of passengers are about 15 years old or younger.\n",
        "\"\"\"\n",
        "\n",
        "age_q1 = np.quantile(data['Age'], 0.25)\n",
        "age_q2 = np.quantile(data['Age'], 0.50)\n",
        "age_q3 = np.quantile(data['Age'], 0.75)\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "bWl5UlBlBRZ2"
      },
      "execution_count": 4,
      "outputs": []
    },
